                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan></supplied> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avio</ex></expan> Crescen<lb break="no" n="2"/>tino <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avii</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>fil</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> II et <expan><abbr>Claud</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Crescentino <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>iti</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XIIII <expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex>eminae</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XXV <expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> X <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avius</ex></expan> Secundinus <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>eiusd</abbr><ex>em</ex></expan> <lb n="10"/>filio et <expan><abbr>socer</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zeile 1 befindet sich im Hauptbild oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes neben dem Kranz. Zeile 3: TI-Ligatur; Zeile 4: ET-, AV-Ligatur, D klein am Zeilenende; Zeile 5: NTI-Ligatur, O klein am Zeilenende in oberem Winkel des N; Zeile 7: TI-Ligatur; Zeile 8: kleines S am Zeilenende in V eingeschrieben; Zeile 10: ET-Ligatur. Im Hauptbild oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes Kranz mit Tänien, Rosetten; das Inschriftfeld von Weinranken eingefasst. (B): CIL 03, 04467; Krüger: Z.7: AN XXX STIP X.</p>
            </div>
